title._content: Color enhancement of image of earth photographed by UV camera

description._content: Collection: NASA Johnson Space Center Collection Title: Color enhancement of image of earth photographed by UV camera Description: A color enhancement of an ultraviolet photograph of the geocorona, a halo of low density hydrogen around the Earth. Sunlight is shining from the left, and the geocorona is brighter on that side. The UV camera was operated by Astronaut John W. Young on the Apollo 16 lunar landing mission.
